								<!-- bodycontent -->
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p><b>Ben Margulies</b> is a <a href="Grammy" title="Grammy" class="mw-redirect">Grammy</a> nominated <a href="Songwriter" title="Songwriter">songwriter</a> and a <a href="Recording_Industry_Association_of_America" title="Recording Industry Association of America">RIAA</a> nine-time platinum certified <a href="Record_producer" title="Record producer">record producer</a>. He is best known for co-writing, arranging, and producing <a href="Mariah_Carey" title="Mariah Carey">Mariah Carey</a>'s self-titled debut album.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc">
<tr>
<td>
<div id="toctitle">
